{"title": "Introduction to Active Directory", "source": "htb-academy", "source_label": "HTB Academy", "path": "Active Directory/Introduction to Active Directory", "html": "<h2 id=\"general-module-commands\">General Module Commands</h2>\n<p>Basic PowerShell and Active Directory module commands for getting oriented in a domain environment.</p>\n<h3 id=\"get-loaded-powershell-modules\">Get Loaded PowerShell Modules</h3>\n<p>Lists all currently loaded PowerShell modules, their version, and available commands.</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-Module</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"list-commands-for-a-module\">List Commands for a Module</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-Command</span> <span class=\"n\">-Module</span> <span class=\"n\">ActiveDirectory</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"get-help-on-a-cmdlet\">Get Help on a Cmdlet</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-Help</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">cmdlet</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"import-the-active-directory-module\">Import the Active Directory Module</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Import-Module</span> <span class=\"n\">ActiveDirectory</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"rdp-to-a-target\">RDP to a Target</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>xfreerdp<span class=\"w\"> </span>/v:&lt;target-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>/u:&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>/p:&lt;password&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"run-a-command-as-another-user\">Run a Command as Another User</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>runas /netonly /user:&lt;domain&gt;\\&lt;username&gt; powershell\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"ad-user-commands\">AD User Commands</h2>\n<h3 id=\"create-a-new-ad-user\">Create a New AD User</h3>\n<p>Creates a new user with a secure password and sets additional attributes.</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">New-ADUser</span> <span class=\"n\">-Name</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;firstname&gt; &lt;lastname&gt;&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Accountpassword</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nb\">Read-Host</span> <span class=\"n\">-AsSecureString</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;Super$ecurePassword!&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"n\">-Enabled</span> <span class=\"nv\">$true</span> <span class=\"n\">-OtherAttributes</span> <span class=\"p\">@{</span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;title&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Analyst&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">;</span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;mail&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;f.last@&lt;domain&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"remove-an-ad-user\">Remove an AD User</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Remove-ADUser</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">username</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"unlock-an-ad-account\">Unlock an AD Account</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Unlock-ADAccount</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">username</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"reset-a-users-password\">Reset a User's Password</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Set-ADAccountPassword</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;username&gt;&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Reset</span> <span class=\"n\">-NewPassword</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nb\">ConvertTo-SecureString</span> <span class=\"n\">-AsPlainText</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;NewP@ssw0rdReset!&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Force</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"force-password-change-at-next-logon\">Force Password Change at Next Logon</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Set-ADUser</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">username</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-ChangePasswordAtLogon</span> <span class=\"nv\">$true</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"ad-group-ou-commands\">AD Group &amp; OU Commands</h2>\n<h3 id=\"create-an-organizational-unit\">Create an Organizational Unit</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">New-ADOrganizationalUnit</span> <span class=\"n\">-Name</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;name&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Path</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;OU=folder,DC=&lt;domain&gt;,DC=local&quot;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"create-a-security-group\">Create a Security Group</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">New-ADGroup</span> <span class=\"n\">-Name</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;name&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-SamAccountName</span> <span class=\"n\">analysts</span> <span class=\"n\">-GroupCategory</span> <span class=\"n\">Security</span> <span class=\"n\">-GroupScope</span> <span class=\"n\">Global</span> <span class=\"n\">-DisplayName</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;Security Analysts&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Path</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;CN=Users,DC=&lt;domain&gt;,DC=local&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Description</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;Members of this group are Security Analysts under the IT OU&quot;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"add-users-to-a-group\">Add Users to a Group</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Add-ADGroupMember</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;group name&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Members</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;user1,user2,user3&#39;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"gpo-commands\">GPO Commands</h2>\n<h3 id=\"copy-a-gpo\">Copy a GPO</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Copy-GPO</span> <span class=\"n\">-SourceName</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;GPO to copy&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-TargetName</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;Name&quot;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"link-a-gpo-to-an-ou\">Link a GPO to an OU</h3>\n<p>Links an existing GPO to the specified OU path and enables it.</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">New-GPLink</span> <span class=\"n\">-Name</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;Security Analysts Control&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Target</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;ou=Security Analysts,ou=IT,OU=HQ-NYC,OU=Employees,OU=Corp,dc=&lt;domain&gt;,dc=LOCAL&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-LinkEnabled</span> <span class=\"n\">Yes</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"modify-a-gpo-link\">Modify a GPO Link</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Set-GPLink</span> <span class=\"n\">-Name</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;Security Analysts Control&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Target</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;ou=Security Analysts,ou=IT,OU=HQ-NYC,OU=Employees,OU=Corp,dc=&lt;domain&gt;,dc=LOCAL&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-LinkEnabled</span> <span class=\"n\">Yes</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"computer-account-commands\">Computer Account Commands</h2>\n<h3 id=\"add-a-computer-to-the-domain\">Add a Computer to the Domain</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Add-Computer</span> <span class=\"n\">-DomainName</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;DOMAIN&gt;&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Credential</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;DOMAIN&gt;\\&lt;username&gt;&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Restart</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"remotely-add-a-computer-to-a-domain\">Remotely Add a Computer to a Domain</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Add-Computer</span> <span class=\"n\">-ComputerName</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;name&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-LocalCredential</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;.\\localuser&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-DomainName</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;DOMAIN&gt;&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Credential</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;DOMAIN&gt;\\&lt;username&gt;&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Restart</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"check-computer-properties\">Check Computer Properties</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-ADComputer</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;name&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Properties</span> <span class=\"p\">*</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">select </span><span class=\"n\">CN</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">CanonicalName</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">IPv4Address</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"useful-ldap-queries\">Useful LDAP Queries</h2>\n<h3 id=\"list-all-ad-groups-via-ldap-filter\">List All AD Groups via LDAP Filter</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-ADObject</span> <span class=\"n\">-LDAPFilter</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;(objectClass=group)&#39;</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">select </span><span class=\"n\">cn</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"list-disabled-users\">List Disabled Users</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-ADUser</span> <span class=\"n\">-LDAPFilter</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;(userAccountControl:1.2.840.113556.1.4.803:=2)&#39;</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">select </span><span class=\"n\">name</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"count-users-in-an-ou\">Count Users in an OU</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nb\">Get-ADUser</span> <span class=\"n\">-SearchBase</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;OU=Employees,DC=&lt;DOMAIN&gt;,DC=LOCAL&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Filter</span> <span class=\"p\">*).</span><span class=\"n\">count</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"find-computers-by-hostname-pattern\">Find Computers by Hostname Pattern</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-ADComputer</span> <span class=\"n\">-Filter</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;DNSHostName -like &#39;SQL*&#39;&quot;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"get-all-administrative-groups\">Get All Administrative Groups</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-ADGroup</span> <span class=\"n\">-Filter</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;adminCount -eq 1&quot;</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">select </span><span class=\"n\">Name</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"find-admin-users-without-kerberos-pre-auth\">Find Admin Users Without Kerberos Pre-Auth</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-ADUser</span> <span class=\"n\">-Filter</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"n\">adminCount</span> <span class=\"o\">-eq</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;1&#39;</span> <span class=\"o\">-and</span> <span class=\"n\">DoesNotRequirePreAuth</span> <span class=\"o\">-eq</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;True&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"enumerate-uac-values-for-admin-users\">Enumerate UAC Values for Admin Users</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-ADUser</span> <span class=\"n\">-Filter</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"n\">adminCount</span> <span class=\"o\">-gt</span> <span class=\"n\">0</span><span class=\"p\">}</span> <span class=\"n\">-Properties</span> <span class=\"n\">admincount</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">useraccountcontrol</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"get-ad-groups-via-wmi\">Get AD Groups via WMI</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-WmiObject</span> <span class=\"n\">-Class</span> <span class=\"n\">win32_group</span> <span class=\"n\">-Filter</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;Domain=&#39;&lt;DOMAIN&gt;&#39;&quot;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"search-for-all-computers-via-adsi\">Search for All Computers via ADSI</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"no\">[adsisearcher]</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;(&amp;(objectClass=Computer))&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">).</span><span class=\"n\">FindAll</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"query-installed-software\">Query Installed Software</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">get-ciminstance</span> <span class=\"n\">win32_product</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">fl</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"check-rsat-tools\">Check RSAT Tools</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-WindowsCapability</span> <span class=\"n\">-Name</span> <span class=\"n\">RSAT</span><span class=\"p\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">-Online</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">Select-Object</span> <span class=\"n\">-Property</span> <span class=\"n\">Name</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">State</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"install-all-rsat-tools\">Install All RSAT Tools</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-WindowsCapability</span> <span class=\"n\">-Name</span> <span class=\"n\">RSAT</span><span class=\"p\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">-Online</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">Add-WindowsCapability</span> <span class=\"n\">-Online</span>\n</code></pre></div>", "excerpt": "General Module Commands Basic PowerShell and Active Directory module commands for getting oriented in a domain environment. Get Loaded PowerShell Modules Lists all currently loaded PowerShell modules,", "tags": []}